{"tid":1665690,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[教學] 和理非 請進化","createTime":"2019-10-20T16:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T12:48:49.000Z","uid":73143,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae37cefc3deaf45b5b0709134471ce9f6b1aec2","tid":1665690,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:06:21.000Z","msg":"鑑於今日仲有好多未進化既和理非，所以要開返個post比和理非學習進化下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1. 唔好放車入</strong></span></span><br />\n黑警而家係可以徵用其他部門既車輛 (包括但不限於：消防、救護)<br />\n仲有大量既私家車、貨車、van仔、小巴<br />\n之前有好多手足因為咁樣而比狗拉走左<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>反抗唔係口號，請塞滿成條馬路<br />\n而唔係行人路上面不停「香港人，反抗」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n貨車<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8PKl5IV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8PKl5IV.jpg&h=7f9f931b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pn79ot0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPn79ot0.gif&h=d48a1ca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n康文van仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TecLHyl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTecLHyl.jpg&h=62cb70bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防車<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/paynJPN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpaynJPN.jpg&h=df915f8d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n救護車<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rrLf73C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrrLf73C.jpg&h=fc2757fd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n私家車<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VNYhQ3Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVNYhQ3Q.png&h=ec1b0f7f&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n放車入黎之後撞斷手足雙腿<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/pi19m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fpi19m&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=c62e64d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/pi19m</a><br />\n<br />\n［我係消防處屬員］請大家抗爭時盡情阻擋消防/救護車輛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1660645/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1660645/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 落雨主動開遮</span></strong></span><br />\n好多和理非企係到唔知做乜<br />\n見到手足做野、神獸、裝修都唔識開遮<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住，開遮係遮樣 遮鏡頭，而唔係遮佢做緊d乜</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UMavBa5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUMavBa5.jpg&h=7a141c19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>3. 真 不割席</strong></span></span><br />\n唔好下下有手足做野就話係狗做<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地口講唔割席，但咁樣都割席有咩分別？</span></span></strong><br />\n除非真係明顯得濟好似觀塘燒站咁比記者影到哂<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/L78cTVi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FL78cTVi.png&h=53dc7fa0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n <br />\n其實呢d都講過好多次，下面比d可參考既post和理非<br />\n<br />\n《和理升級教戰手冊》入門篇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1613246/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1613246/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"3a0f068ac19b5b0f9a43a7c1b9435853e508b4cd","tid":1665690,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91383dfdc1631c5e404617b762c370c62168bca","tid":1665690,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be421f8526624a95dca09e6c4a8df0baf38f7bb3","tid":1665690,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71e2bfb205da67a81a0ff5733a7d67c114d774f","tid":1665690,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3498fd04818ea0de72c513f72afa1190f077fd","tid":1665690,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:24:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96b5f72ef86ae05a18c894ec46517d58745e6a55","tid":1665690,"uid":42149,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:26:24.000Z","msg":"仲有，唔好亂咁鳩叫行快啲，要走同前線講<br />\n唔好自己係咁走然後留低前線<br />\n<br />\n唔好覺得危險就走，由上個月開始，所有遊行都係非法，所有野有危險。<br />\n記住，人多就係優勢，散野就死硬"},{"pid":"fc6065e1151e50730075d4cc10c64f4bef05abb3","tid":1665690,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478ecdd75c1f03b02841406bbb7f92947a7e59af","tid":1665690,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:28:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133fb572d09ed0d6372c34dae01ad866c96bf6fb","tid":1665690,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:32:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f875f724116c7ef4dcf9cfe1ae35846e3416a2f5","tid":1665690,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:35:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b793eff9b746a3f2d5fda69a303d673e302b82d2","tid":1665690,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T16:35:28.000Z","msg":"第2樣今日好多和理非有做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a7bceb52cb0b